Articles.Content:
Ah! Good to see this mod was adopted. Great mod idea, but unfortunately too buggy back then, so I've dropped it. May try it again in the future, if\when OPM gets a graphic upgrade (currently I'm on KSRSS 16K, and damn that looks gorgeous)

Edited September 24, 2021 by biohazard15
Exo may be working on her own outer planet mod, so I'll be making sure to make patches for when that comes out.

Version 1.1.3 is out! Featuring...

  • DDS textures
  • Proper Geito normal map
  • Removed redundant files
  • Science defs for magnetometers (stock/DMagic) [WIP]

Version 1.1.5 is out; a bugfix for 1.1.3.

* Flake now has a texture.
* Lon no longer has Gilly's texture.
Cool. While your at it, revamp Gilly's texture and height map. Gilly is really bland and only reason to go there as of now is either re-fueling or just fun jetpacking around.

3 hours ago, MCWither_Storm said:

Cool. While your at it, revamp Gilly's texture and height map. Gilly is really bland and only reason to go there as of now is either re-fueling or just fun jetpacking around.

This is an expansion, not an overhaul. Completely revamping Gilly is outside of the scope of this specific mod, but if you're into doing it yourself that's perfectly fine.

17 hours ago, Interplanet Janet said:

This is an expansion, not an overhaul. Completely revamping Gilly is outside of the scope of this specific mod, but if you're into doing it yourself that's perfectly fine.

Noted.  One thing that is a pain is that the smaller bodies need stupid precise maneuvers to enter their SOI, which are as low as around 31 kilometers.

Noted.  One thing that is a pain is that the smaller bodies need stupid precise maneuvers to enter their SOI, which are as low as around 31 kilometers.
